Shelby Anthony VOGT, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
John OGDEN, Denice Bennett, and University Studios, Defendants-Appellees. No. 18-0824 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Plaintiff appeals the district court's dismissal of his petition in a landlord-tenant dispute. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
